---
name: workers
description: Check status of all worker terminals
user-invocable: true
version: "1.0.0"
---

# Worker Status Dashboard

Display current status of all worker terminals.

## Live Status

### Progress Tracker
```bash
cat .agent/prompts/_progress.yaml 2>/dev/null
```

### Pending Tasks
```bash
echo "=== PENDING ===" && ls -la .agent/prompts/pending/ 2>/dev/null || echo "None"
```

### Completed Tasks
```bash
echo "=== COMPLETED ===" && ls -la .agent/prompts/completed/ 2>/dev/null | tail -10
```

### Recent Activity Log
```bash
echo "=== RECENT LOGS ===" && tail -20 .agent/logs/prompt_lifecycle.log 2>/dev/null || echo "No logs"
```

## Output Format

Summarize in this format:

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ WORKER STATUS DASHBOARD                                  │
├───────────┬──────────┬──────────────────────────────────┤
│ Terminal  │ Status   │ Current Task                     │
├───────────┼──────────┼──────────────────────────────────┤
│ B         │ {status} │ {task or "idle"}                 │
│ C         │ {status} │ {task or "idle"}                 │
│ D         │ {status} │ {task or "idle"}                 │
└───────────┴──────────┴──────────────────────────────────┘

Completed: {n} tasks
Pending: {n} tasks
Blocked: {list or "none"}

Next Action: {recommendation}
```

## Recommendations

Based on status, suggest:
- If workers idle + pending tasks → "Assign pending tasks"
- If all complete → "Run E2E verification"
- If blocked → "Resolve {blocker} first"
